<br>
Those of us that were on late Monday night decided that a guild meeting is in order for those of us who are left.  At this meeting, we will <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  /random 100</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> for the title of <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Guild-leader</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  This roll will include the new officers, and a few others that we deem fit to roll for the title.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Date: Friday, October 6<br>
Time: 9:00pm Eastern, 8:00 Central<br>
Location: Lesser Faydark - entrance to Mistmoore Castle</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Also, reassignment of guild officers will take place.  At this point, I would like to name our officers.  They will be:<br>
<br>
1. Valmar<br>
2. Khoal<br>
3. Ndirya<br>
4. Elbrian/Shodean, etc.<br>
5. Giradella/Desiduous, etc.<br>
6. Atacand<br>
<br>
Other officers may be named at a later date.<br>
<br>
A new recruiting policy is in order as well.  As officers, we will not actively recruit anyone who is lower than level 10.  However, if an individual comes to us wanting to join, they will be admitted into the guild.  This policy will remain in effect until the officers feel that our numbers are strong enough to slow the influx of new members.<br>
<br>
Please periodically remind people in guildchat of the meeting.  At this point, we do not have anyone who can teleport.  Maybe I can convince Kiglan to loan us Kidwan for a few ports.<br>
<br>
See you all online.<br>
